title.rendered: MARK KENLY DOMINO TAN AW24 during Copenhagen Fashion Week

content.rendered:
MARK KENLY DOMINO TAN Fall-Winter 2024 COLLECTION at Copenhagen Fashion Week

Impeccable quality and craftsmanship are at the heart and soul of the Mark Kenly Domino Tan Studio aesthetic. The tailored Atelier collections, made according to the couture tradition, can be found in the adjacent design studio in central Copenhagen.

Mark Kenly Domino Tan Studio's sustainability lies within the timeless design, crafting a closet full of long-lasting pieces that survive season after season.

Cut from carefully sourced, natural fabrics, each is selected for its beauty and durability, as well as its ability to alter in expression when shaped and combined in new ways.

Extending the life of fashion garments is crucial for a more sustainable production and consumption and serves as one of Mark Kenly Domino Tan's core values.

Runway Looks

Photo: Press Mark Kenly Domino Tan

More on: @mkdtstudio


By Senior Fashion Editor 24FashionTV: Christina V Henningstad @christina_henningstad
